data.enText: a person whose job involves examining facts or materials in order to give an opinion on them

data.chText: 政治分析家；食物化验员

data.enText: City analysts forecast huge profits this year.
data.chText: 伦敦金融分析家预测今年的利润非常丰厚。

tr: someone who is skilled at analyzing data
an expert who studies financial data (on credit or securities or sales or financial patterns etc.) and recommends appropriate business actions

value.def: An analyst is a person whose job is to analyse a subject and give opinions about it.
An analyst is someone, usually a doctor, who examines and treats people who are emotionally disturbed.
